Louise Latham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louise_Latham 0 Louise Latham (September 23, 1922 – February 12, 2018) was an American actress, perhaps best known for her portrayal of Bernice Edgar in Alfred Hitchcock's 1964 film Marnie.
